@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #82668 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

This looks like an intended change where we catch more cases of attributes being applied to the wrong things. Also:

Filing primarily so that we can get this documented in release notes as a compatibility note (if it isn't already)

So I think we should remove I-prioritize.
